{"tid":2129082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★零售管理協會：業主以法律行動迫使租戶全數繳租 憂出現大規模結業及裁員潮。","createTime":"2020-07-28T10:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T09:41:47.000Z","uid":19454,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"68c8513f9d5f15a927c6d4ed73e083d6eaa902d3","tid":2129082,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:58:43.000Z","msg":"香港零售管理協會在報章刊登廣告，向本港商舖業主發公開信，呼籲他們對暫時無法繳付租金的商戶，停止採取任何法律手段或收回店舖，為期不少於9個月。<br />\n<br />\n協會亦呼籲業主取消底租，按租戶營業額收取分成租金，為期9至12個月，以免6萬多間店舖陷入結業危機，影響超過26萬名從業員及他們家人的生計。<br />\n<br />\n協會指出，零售業過去一年多受到社會事件及新型冠狀病毒打擊，收入跌超過一半甚至八成，但承擔比現時租值貴一倍或更高的租金。<br />\n<br />\n協會表示，很多業主自4月陸續收緊對商舖的租金支援，大部分店舖已不獲減租，有業主以法律行動迫使租戶全數繳租，或以續約作為租金紓緩條件，擔憂政府的保就業計劃完結前，業界已出現大規模結業及裁員潮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540277-20200728.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540277-20200728.htm&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD6%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=1f216830\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540277-20200728.htm&h=a4f3fa9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540277-20200728.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b6b623c57ebe21661203acf1ae528d57013f6541","tid":2129082,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ff15fdfcf299ea8ac5ff45c552954dd203ccf0","tid":2129082,"uid":156652,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"68c8513f9d5f15a927c6d4ed73e083d6eaa902d3","tid":2129082,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"